    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="1、首页工作台问题"><a href="#1、首页工作台问题" class="headerlink" title="1、首页工作台问题"></a>1、首页工作台问题</h3><p>【工作台】中点击没有挂载报表的【四个模块】后，系统中其他菜单触发无效<br>修改办法：–&gt;找到人大包相应路径文件【npcs-web-8.30\npcs\functionPages\workbench_cp】，将以下代码更改</p>
<p>更改前：</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*打开页签*/</span></span><br><span class="line">        budgetClick: function(item) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                   parent.$addTab(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	                menuId: item.AREA_CODE,</span><br><span class="line">	                menuName: item.AREA_NAME,</span><br><span class="line">	                url: item.URL,</span><br><span class="line">	                menuLogo: ''</span><br><span class="line">	            &#125;);         </span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>更改后：</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*打开页签*/</span></span><br><span class="line">        budgetClick: function(item) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        	if(item.AREA_CODE)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                     parent.$addTab(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	                menuId: item.AREA_CODE,</span><br><span class="line">	                menuName: item.AREA_NAME,</span><br><span class="line">	                url: item.URL,</span><br><span class="line">	                menuLogo: ''</span><br><span class="line">	            &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">        	&#125;            </span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="2、审查菜单配置"><a href="#2、审查菜单配置" class="headerlink" title="2、审查菜单配置"></a>2、审查菜单配置</h3><p>【菜单审查配置】中【业务分类】无法更换问题：<br>解决办法：–&gt;找到人大包相应路径文件【\npcs\menuandshowplan\menuandshowplan.js】，将以下代码【覆盖】原始代码</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">getPlanLbRela:function(showPlan_id,selectFlag)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                var that = this;</span><br><span class="line">                axios.get("/ywgl/getPlanByMenu",&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    params:&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        menuid:that.menudata.menu_id,</span><br><span class="line">                        subject_id:that.version_id</span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;).then(function(res)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    var data = res.data;</span><br><span class="line">                    if(data.errorCode=='1')&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        that.delScMlList=[];</span><br><span class="line">                        if(data.showplanList&amp;&amp;data.showplanList.length&amp;&amp;!selectFlag)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                         that.showPlanData=data.showplanList[0];</span><br><span class="line">                            that.assignFrom(that.showPlanData);</span><br><span class="line">                        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                        that.ywScMlList=data.reviewLbList;</span><br><span class="line">                        that.ywScMlIdList=[];</span><br><span class="line">                        for(var i = 0;i&lt;that.ywScMlList.length;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                            that.ywScMlIdList.push(that.ywScMlList[i].LB_ID);</span><br><span class="line">                        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                        // this.handleSelect(this.curYwId);</span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        that.$message(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                            message: "查询失败",</span><br><span class="line">                            type: 'warning'</span><br><span class="line">                        &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;).catch(function(e)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3、报表弹窗重影"><a href="#3、报表弹窗重影" class="headerlink" title="3、报表弹窗重影"></a>3、报表弹窗重影</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">修改相应主题表文件夹的脚本，将对应弹窗中的txt(<span class="string">""</span>)置空</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="4、审查阶段设置"><a href="#4、审查阶段设置" class="headerlink" title="4、审查阶段设置"></a>4、审查阶段设置</h3><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">数据库中对表【<span class="selector-tag">NPCS_SYS_VERSION</span>】中【<span class="selector-tag">IDX_NO</span>】字段进行排序设置，并在<span class="selector-tag">BI</span>中设置相应报表中【审查阶段】如下的默认值。</span><br><span class="line">&lt;#=ardb("SELECT min(T.VERSION_CODE)  FROM NPCS_SYS_VERSION T  WHERE T.PARENT_VERSION_CODE = '"+diminf("审查类别",@sclb,'VERSION_CODE')+"' ORDER BY  T.VERSION_CODE").join(";")#&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="5、修改端口后注意事项"><a href="#5、修改端口后注意事项" class="headerlink" title="5、修改端口后注意事项"></a>5、修改端口后注意事项</h3><h4 id="01、数据库中5个端口"><a href="#01、数据库中5个端口" class="headerlink" title="01、数据库中5个端口"></a>01、数据库中5个端口</h4><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> npcs_module t <span class="keyword">set</span> t.module_url = <span class="keyword">replace</span>(t.module_url,<span class="string">'http://10.82.1.98:7001/bi'</span>,<span class="string">'http://10.82.1.96:7001/bi'</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> npcs_analysis t <span class="keyword">set</span> t.analysis_url = <span class="keyword">replace</span>(t.analysis_url,<span class="string">'http://10.82.1.98:7001/bi'</span>,<span class="string">'http://10.82.1.96:7001/bi'</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> npcs_sys_manage t <span class="keyword">set</span> t.chr_value = <span class="keyword">replace</span>(t.chr_value,<span class="string">'http://10.82.1.98:7001/bi'</span>,<span class="string">'http://10.82.1.96:7001/bi'</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> npcs_portal_area_conf t <span class="keyword">set</span> t.url = <span class="keyword">replace</span>(t.url,<span class="string">'http://192.168.1.8:7001/bi'</span>,<span class="string">'http://10.82.1.96:7001/bi'</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> sys_menu t <span class="keyword">set</span> t.url = <span class="keyword">replace</span>(t.url,<span class="string">'10.10.65.14:8001'</span>,<span class="string">'10.82.1.96:8005'</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> * <span class="keyword">FROM</span> sys_userpara <span class="keyword">WHERE</span> chr_code <span class="keyword">LIKE</span> <span class="string">'NPCS_REPORT_URL%'</span><span class="keyword">for</span> <span class="keyword">update</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="02、BI中分析与展现–-gt-公式模块的端口"><a href="#02、BI中分析与展现–-gt-公式模块的端口" class="headerlink" title="02、BI中分析与展现–&gt;公式模块的端口"></a>02、BI中<font color="gree">分析与展现</font>–&gt;<font color="gree">公式模块</font>的端口</h4><h3 id="6、BI"><a href="#6、BI" class="headerlink" title="6、BI"></a>6、BI</h3><h4 id="01、版本问题"><a href="#01、版本问题" class="headerlink" title="01、版本问题"></a>01、版本问题</h4><p>一般我们拿到的都是预算批复的数据，为了防止点其他版本的时候数据显示的问题，所以需要进行如下设置：<br>在报表上面的参数栏里添加两个参数，一个是<font color="gree">数据版本</font>，参数名为<font color="gree">@data_version</font>。一个是<font color="gree">默认版本</font>，参数名是<font color="gree">@mrbb</font>，默认值要这样设置:</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">a</span>.默认版本：</span><br><span class="line">&lt;#=ardb('select max(data_version) from V_NPCS_WARNING_FB_RPT').max()#&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">b</span>.浮动维的过滤条件里面也要加上语句：</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">if</span>(<span class="keyword">@data_version</span>=''|<span class="keyword">@data_version</span>='null'|<span class="keyword">@data_version</span>='undefined',V_NPCS_WARNING_FB_RPT.DATA_VERSION=<span class="keyword">@mrbb</span>,V_NPCS_WARNING_FB_RPT.DATA_VERSION=<span class="keyword">@data_version</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>注：将语句中的<font color="gree">主题表</font>改成相应的主题表。</p>
<h4 id="02、系统中表明显示业务类型"><a href="#02、系统中表明显示业务类型" class="headerlink" title="02、系统中表明显示业务类型"></a>02、系统中表明显示业务类型</h4><p>在BI中触发一下相应主体域的<font color="gree">维表</font></p>
<h3 id="7、预警"><a href="#7、预警" class="headerlink" title="7、预警"></a>7、预警</h3><h4 id="01、预警图片"><a href="#01、预警图片" class="headerlink" title="01、预警图片"></a>01、预警图片</h4><p>str1，flag添加 设置字符型  没有flag需要添加flag字段<br>str2，修改图片前缀</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if(Q4=9,'',if(Q4 IN [2,3,4],'vfs/root/products/ebi/sys/picture/绿色.png',if(O4=1,'vfs/root/products/ebi/sys/picture/蓝色.png',IF(O4=2,'vfs/root/products/ebi/sys/picture/黄色.png',IF(O4=3,'vfs/root/products/ebi/sys/picture/红色.png','')))))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="02、预警提示"><a href="#02、预警提示" class="headerlink" title="02、预警提示"></a>02、预警提示</h4><p><img src="/2020/06/23/a/C:%5CFAN-MOMO%5Chexo%5Csource_posts%5Ca%5C%E9%A2%84%E8%AD%A6%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA.jpg" alt></p>
<p>常见模板：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">时序过快：</span><br><span class="line">[项目名称]||<span class="string">'本月累计完成数为'</span>||[累计完成数]||<span class="string">'万元，本月止累计为预算数为'</span>||[累计为预算数]||<span class="string">'%，实际完成进度高于序时进度'</span>||ROUND([累计为预算数]-[月份]/12*100，2)||<span class="string">'%,超出阀值30%。计算公式：累计为预算数-本月月份/12*100%'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">时序过慢：</span><br><span class="line">[项目名称]||<span class="string">'本月累计完成数为'</span>||[累计完成数]||<span class="string">'万元，本月止累计为预算数为'</span>||[累计为预算数]||<span class="string">'%，实际完成进度低于序时进度'</span>||ROUND([累计为预算数]-[月份]/12*100，2)||<span class="string">'%,超出阀值30%。计算公式：累计为预算数-本月月份/12*100%'</span></span><br><span class="line">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">比上年同期降幅较大：</span><br><span class="line">[项目名称]||<span class="string">'本月累计完成数为'</span>||[累计完成数]||<span class="string">'万元，上年同期完成数为'</span>||[累计上年同期数]||<span class="string">'万元，本月累计完成数低于上年同期完成数'</span>||[累计同比]||<span class="string">'%，超出阀值30%。计算公式：（本月累计完成数-上年同期完成数）/上年同期完成数*100%'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">比上年同期增幅较大：</span><br><span class="line">[项目名称]||<span class="string">'本月累计完成数为'</span>||[累计完成数]||<span class="string">'万元，上年同期完成数为'</span>||[累计上年同期数]||<span class="string">'万元，本月累计完成数高于上年同期完成数'</span>||[累计同比]||<span class="string">'%，超出阀值30%。计算公式：（本月累计完成数-上年同期完成数）/上年同期完成数*100%'</span></span><br><span class="line">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">执行数不足预算数：</span><br><span class="line">[项目名称]||<span class="string">'执行数为'</span>||[执行数]||<span class="string">'万元，年初预算数为'</span>||[预算数]||<span class="string">'万元，执行数为预算数的'</span>||[执行数比预算数]||<span class="string">'%，低于阀值70%。计算公式：预算数/执行数*100%'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">执行数超出预算数：</span><br><span class="line">[项目名称]||<span class="string">'执行数为'</span>||[执行数]||<span class="string">'万元，年初预算数为'</span>||[预算数]||<span class="string">'万元，执行数为预算数的'</span>||[执行数比预算数]||<span class="string">'%，超出阀值70%。计算公式：预算数/执行数*100%'</span></span><br><span class="line">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">执行数超出调整预算数：</span><br><span class="line">[项目名称]||<span class="string">'执行数为'</span>||[执行数]||<span class="string">'万元，调整预算数为'</span>||[预算调整数]||<span class="string">'万元，执行数为调整预算数'</span>||[执行数比预算调整数]||<span class="string">'%，超出阀值130%。计算公式：执行数/调整预算数*100%'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">执行数不足调整预算数：</span><br><span class="line">[项目名称]||<span class="string">'执行数为'</span>||[执行数]||<span class="string">'万元，调整预算数为'</span>||[预算调整数]||<span class="string">'万元，执行数为调整预算数'</span>||[执行数比预算调整数]||<span class="string">'%，低于阀值130%。计算公式：执行数/调整预算数*100%'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="8、清除weblogic缓存"><a href="#8、清除weblogic缓存" class="headerlink" title="8、清除weblogic缓存"></a>8、清除<font color="gree">weblogic</font>缓存</h3><p>删除相应域的对应文件夹</p>
